query:
SELECT 
  district,
  priceYen,
  priceYen / 10000 as price_man,
  buildingAreaM2,
  (priceYen / 10000) / buildingAreaM2 as price_per_sqm_man,
  buildingYear,
  nearestStation,
  stationDistanceMin
FROM transactions
WHERE prefecture = '神奈川県' 
  AND city = '横浜市中区' 
  AND propertyType = 'マンション'
LIMIT 10;
